  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00196', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-111-3082b5f1', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-07', NULL, 'essay', '臺中市政府建設局依臺中市道路挖掘管理自治條例第 2條規定，為該自
