  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00197', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-111-3082b5f1', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-07', NULL, 'essay', '甲向主管機關 A申請興建節能設備之補助，A所提供之申請表中特別註
