  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00198', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-111-3082b5f1', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-07', NULL, 'essay', '甲公立學校乙班學生於學校外掃區域打掃，學生A拾獲棒球後，以掃把
